attempts.sparql_query:
PREFIX nas: <http://www.semanticdesktop.org/ontologies/2007/04/18/nas#> 
SELECT ?seatCount1 ?seatCount2
WHERE {
    nas:AAL1170 nas:numberOfSeats ?seatCount1 .
    nas:ASA14 nas:numberOfSeats ?seatCount2 .
    FILTER (?seatCount1 = ?seatCount2)
}
attempts.query_explanation: This SPARQL query checks if the number of seats on board for flights AAL1170 and ASA14 are equal.
